<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ر ز ز<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٢٠٨٩ - ر ز ز]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>رزَّزَ يُرزِّز، ترزيزًا، فهو مُرزِّز، والمفعول مُرزَّز<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• رزَّز الطَّعامَ:</span> صنَعه بالأُرز.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• رزَّز الشَّيءَ:</span> ثبَّته <span class="c1">"رزَّز القفلَ بالباب"</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>